msgstr "siete stati trattenuti sulla strada per Dunwich."

msgid "Each investigator who was defeated has acquired the Across Space and Time weakness and must add 1 copy of it to their deck. This card does not count toward that investigator’s deck size."
msgstr "Ogni investigatore sconfitto aggiunge 1 Attraverso lo Spazio e il Tempo al suo mazzo (non considerandolo nella dimensione del suo mazzo)."

msgid "Each investigator who was defeated earns 1 bonus experience as their experience beyond the gate grants them insight into the cosmos."
msgstr "Ogni investigatore sconfitto guadagna 1 punto esperienza a causa della rivelazione improvvisa del cosmo scoperta oltre il portale."

